Tags:
  - Union-Identity=Mysterium Magnum=The Trackless Trace
By: Ruysbroeck
---
That measureless Splendour of God, which together with the incomprehensible
brightness, is the cause of all gifts and of all virtues -- that same
Uncomprehended Light transfigures the fruitive tendency of our spirit and
penetrates it in a way that is wayless.
